name: First photograph of the Mariana Snailfish - the world's deepest fish
description:
The first photograph ever taken of the world's deepest fish, the Mariana Snailfish (Pseudoliparis swirei) from the scientists who took it. Cropped and edited versions of this image have been released but this unedited raw data is as it came from the lander vehicle and has never been shared before. 
Discovery:
https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0967063716300656
Description:
https://www.mapress.com/zt/article/view/zootaxa.4358.1.7
World record:
https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/deepest-fish

The verified owners of this NFT are entitled to ‘behind the scenes’ media about the find which has never been released.

As well as the above, the first to purchase this NFT will be invited to an in-person experience to be arranged based on their geographical location. 

To claim contact: info@armatusoceanic.com
